OL,3,C'Stomach churning abuse': New law
OL,4,Cdemanded to protect care home residents
OL,6,FSurrey Police investigated but no-one
OL,7,Fwas charged with committing a crime.
OL,9,FFreedom of Information requests by ITV
OL,10,FNews revealed there is a charge rate
OL,11,Fof just 1.4% for allegations of this
OL,12,Fkind.
OL,14,FThe 16 forces which responded told us
OL,15,Fthey had received 1,080 allegations in
OL,16,F2022 - but just 16 charges were made.
OL,18,FRichard and Clare have been
OL,19,Fcampaigning for change after learning
OL,20,Fhow widespread the problem is.
